>JD: ?EENNTV 13A VENET.aN +70 364
#note JD: it's pretty interesting how much better VENETIAN is than REINVENT. Even though REINVENT doesn't give much back, there is one massive hotspot on the board, and after Jeremy covers it I won't get much. VENETIAN actually seems to work out better because it creates multiple places to score, so less likely that Jeremy scores 50 and ties the game. Q even likes EVENTING at 13A, which seems crazy.
